<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HPVCA — Science Illustration System</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --purple-deep: #3A1057;
    --purple: #5E2585;
    --purple-mid: #7B3BA8;
    --purple-light: #A06AC4;
    --lavender: #C9A4E2;
    --lavender-soft: #E8D5F5;
    --lavender-bg: #F5EEFB;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --gray-100: #F4F3F6;
    --gray-400: #9E99A7;
    --gray-500: #6E6878;
    --gray-900: #1A1522;
    --sans: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: var(--sans); color: var(--gray-900); background: var(--white); }

  .page-header { padding: 60px 40px 40px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .page-header p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 700px; }
  .page-header .tag { display: inline-block; background: var(--lavender-bg); color: var(--purple); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 14px; }

  .grid { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 40px 80px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  .card { border: 1px solid #E8E6EC; overflow: hidden; }
  .card.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .card-visual { position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .card-visual.dark { background: var(--purple-deep); }
  .card-visual.light { background: var(--lavender-bg); }
  .card-visual.mid { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--purple-mid) 100%); }
  .card-visual.white-bg { background: var(--white); }
  .card-visual svg { display: block; width: 100%; }
  .card-info { padding: 24px 28px; }
  .card-info h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .card-info .use { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--purple); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .card-info p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.55; }

  .style-notes { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px 80px; }
  .style-notes h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .notes-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .note-card { padding: 28px; background: var(--gray-100); }
  .note-card h4 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--purple); }
  .note-card p { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.6; }
  .note-card .swatch { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .note-card .swatch span { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 4px; }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .card.full { grid-column: auto; }
    .notes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .page-header, .grid, .style-notes { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="tag">HPVCA Visual System</div>
  <h1>Science Illustration Library</h1>
  <p>Organic, biopharma-inspired illustrations for use across the HPVCA website, presentations, and print. Each graphic uses the HPVCA purple/lavender palette and follows a modern life-science visual language — soft cellular forms, molecular structures, flowing connection lines, and radial gradients.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid">

  <!-- 1. HERO ILLUSTRATION — Full-width cellular landscape -->
  <div class="card full">
    <div class="card-visual dark">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 400" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Large organic cell bodies -->
        <ellipse cx="180" cy="200" rx="160" ry="140" fill="url(#h1)" opacity="0.25"/>
        <ellipse cx="500" cy="120" rx="120" ry="100" fill="url(#h2)" opacity="0.2"/>
        <ellipse cx="800" cy="260" rx="180" ry="150" fill="url(#h3)" opacity="0.22"/>
        <ellipse cx="1050" cy="150" rx="140" ry="120" fill="url(#h2)" opacity="0.15"/>
        <ellipse cx="350" cy="320" rx="100" ry="80" fill="url(#h1)" opacity="0.15"/>
        <!-- Cell nuclei -->
        <circle cx="180" cy="190" r="35" fill="url(#h4)" opacity="0.35"/>
        <circle cx="800" cy="250" r="45" fill="url(#h4)" opacity="0.3"/>
        <circle cx="500" cy="115" r="25" fill="url(#h4)" opacity="0.25"/>
        <!-- Molecular bond lines -->
        <path d="M180 200 C300 160 400 140 500 120" stroke="url(#hline)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <path d="M500 120 C600 180 700 220 800 260" stroke="url(#hline)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.12"/>
        <path d="M800 260 C880 220 960 190 1050 150" stroke="url(#hline)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.1"/>
        <path d="M180 200 C240 270 300 300 350 320" stroke="url(#hline)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.1"/>
        <!-- Protein particles -->
        <circle cx="340" cy="160" r="6" fill="#C9A4E2" opacity="0.3"/>
        <circle cx="650" cy="190" r="5" fill="#E8D5F5" opacity="0.25"/>
        <circle cx="920" cy="210" r="7" fill="#A06AC4" opacity="0.2"/>
        <circle cx="250" cy="260" r="4" fill="#E8D5F5" opacity="0.2"/>
        <circle cx="600" cy="300" r="5" fill="#C9A4E2" opacity="0.15"/>
        <circle cx="1000" cy="300" r="6" fill="#A06AC4" opacity="0.15"/>
        <!-- Membrane texture — dashed arcs -->
        <path d="M60 280 Q180 340 300 280" stroke="#C9A4E2" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="4 6" opacity="0.12"/>
        <path d="M700 100 Q800 60 900 100" stroke="#E8D5F5" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="3 5" opacity="0.1"/>
        <path d="M400 350 Q550 380 700 350" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="4 6" opacity="0.08"/>
        <defs>
          <radialGradient id="h1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#C9A4E2"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5E2585" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="h2"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E8D5F5"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#7B3BA8" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="h3"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#A06AC4"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3A1057" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="h4"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E8D5F5" stop-opacity="0.6"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#5E2585" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient>
          <linearGradient id="hline"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="white" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="white"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="white" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="card-info">
      <div class="use">Hero / Page Background</div>
      <h3>Cellular Landscape</h3>
      <p>Full-width illustration showing interconnected cells with nuclei, molecular bond lines, and floating protein particles. Use as hero background on dark purple, or as a decorative backdrop for major sections.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. HPV VIRUS STRUCTURE — Abstract -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-visual light" style="padding: 40px;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Outer capsid shell -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="140" stroke="#5E2585" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="6 4" opacity="0.2"/>
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="120" stroke="#7B3BA8" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.15"/>
        <!-- Pentameric capsomere arrangement (HPV structure) -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="80" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.2"/>
        <!-- L1 protein subunits arranged radially -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="100" r="22" fill="url(#v1)" opacity="0.5"/>
        <circle cx="295" cy="155" r="22" fill="url(#v1)" opacity="0.45"/>
        <circle cx="260" cy="260" r="22" fill="url(#v1)" opacity="0.4"/>
        <circle cx="140" cy="260" r="22" fill="url(#v1)" opacity="0.45"/>
        <circle cx="105" cy="155" r="22" fill="url(#v1)" opacity="0.5"/>
        <!-- Inner ring -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="150" r="14" fill="url(#v2)" opacity="0.35"/>
        <circle cx="245" cy="195" r="14" fill="url(#v2)" opacity="0.3"/>
        <circle cx="228" cy="245" r="14" fill="url(#v2)" opacity="0.28"/>
        <circle cx="172" cy="245" r="14" fill="url(#v2)" opacity="0.3"/>
        <circle cx="155" cy="195" r="14" fill="url(#v2)" opacity="0.35"/>
        <!-- DNA core (circular genome) -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="30" stroke="#5E2585" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.25"/>
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="22" stroke="#7B3BA8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" opacity="0.2"/>
        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="8" fill="#5E2585" opacity="0.3"/>
        <!-- Connection lines from core to capsomeres -->
        <line x1="200" y1="170" x2="200" y2="122" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <line x1="228" y1="190" x2="273" y2="165" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <line x1="220" y1="220" x2="248" y2="248" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <line x1="180" y1="220" x2="152" y2="248" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <line x1="172" y1="190" x2="127" y2="165" stroke="#A06AC4" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/>
        <!-- Floating particles -->
        <circle cx="320" cy="100" r="4" fill="#C9A4E2" opacity="0.3"/>
        <circle cx="80" cy="300" r="5" fill="#E8D5F5" opacity="0.25"/>
        <circle cx="340" cy="310" r="3" fill="#A06AC4" opacity="0.2"/>
        <circle cx="70" cy="110" r="4" fill="#C9A4E2" opacity="0.2"/>
        <defs>
          <radialGradient id="v1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#7B3BA8"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#E8D5F5" stop-opacity="0.1"/></radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="v2"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#A06AC4"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F5EEFB" stop-opacity="0.1"/></radialGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="card-info">
      <div class="use">Card Graphic / Section Art</div>
      <h3>HPV Virus Structure (Abstract)</h3>
      <p>Simplified representation of HPV's icosahedral capsid with L1 protein subunits and circular DNA genome. Scientific but approachable — not clinical. Use for "What is HPV?" cards or educational sections.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. VACCINE / SHIELD CONCEPT -->
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-visual white-bg" style="padding: 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E6EC;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
